     '{"en":{"title":"Broiled Lobster Tail with Garlic Butter","description":"Elegant lobster tails brushed with garlic butter and broiled to perfection — restaurant-quality at home.","ingredients":["Lobster tails — 2-3 tails (each 5-6 oz / 140-170 g)","Unsalted butter, melted — 3 tbsp (42 g)","Garlic, minced — 2-3 cloves","Lemon juice — 1 tbsp","Black pepper — ½ tsp","Paprika (optional, for garnish)"],"directions":["Using kitchen shears, cut through the top shell of each lobster tail down the center, stopping at the tail fan. Lift meat and rest it on top of the shell.","In a small bowl, combine melted butter, garlic, lemon juice, and black pepper.","Brush the garlic-butter mixture generously over lobster meat.","Place tails in the broiler pan, meat side up.","Broil at high heat for 6-10 minutes until opaque and lightly charred."],"tips":["Do not overcook — lobster becomes rubbery quickly.","Watch closely after 6 minutes."]},"es":{"title":"Cola de Langosta a la Parrilla con Mantequilla de Ajo","description":"Elegantes colas de langosta bañadas con mantequilla de ajo y asadas a la perfección — calidad de restaurante en casa.","ingredients":["Colas de langosta — 2-3 colas (cada una 140-170 g)","Mantequilla sin sal, derretida — 3 cdas (42 g)","Ajo, picado — 2-3 dientes","Jugo de limón — 1 cda","Pimienta negra — ½ cdta","Pimentón (opcional, para decorar)"],"directions":["Usando tijeras de cocina, cortar a través de la parte superior de cada cola por el centro, deteniéndose en el abanico. Levantar la carne y dejarla reposar sobre el caparazón.","En un tazón pequeño, combinar la mantequilla derretida, ajo, jugo de limón y pimienta negra.","Cepillar generosamente la mezcla de ajo y mantequilla sobre la carne.","Colocar las colas en la bandeja de la parrilla, lado de la carne hacia arriba.","Asar a fuego alto durante 6-10 minutos hasta que esté opaca y ligeramente chamuscada."],"tips":["No cocine demasiado — la langosta se vuelve gomosa rápidamente.","Vigilar de cerca después de 6 minutos."]},"fr":{"title":"Queue de Homard Grillée au Beurre d Ail","description":"Élégantes queues de homard badigeonnées de beurre à l ail et grillées à la perfection — qualité restaurant à la maison.","ingredients":["Queues de homard — 2-3 queues (chaque 140-170 g)","Beurre doux, fondu — 3 càs (42 g)","Ail, émincé — 2-3 gousses","Jus de citron — 1 càs","Poivre noir — ½ càc","Paprika (optionnel, pour garnir)"],"directions":["Avec des ciseaux de cuisine, couper la carapace supérieure de chaque queue au centre, en s arrêtant à l éventail. Soulever la chair et la reposer sur la carapace.","Dans un petit bol, mélanger le beurre fondu, l ail, le jus de citron et le poivre noir.","Badigeonner généreusement le mélange ail-beurre sur la chair de homard.","Placer les queues dans le plat à griller, chair vers le haut.","Griller à feu vif pendant 6-10 minutes jusqu à ce que la chair soit opaque et légèrement carbonisée."],"tips":["Ne pas trop cuire — le homard devient caoutchouteux rapidement.","Surveiller de près après 6 minutes."]},"ja":{"title":"ガーリックバターブロイルロブスターテール","description":"エレガントなロブスターテールにガーリックバターを塗り、完璧に炙り焼き — 自宅でレストランの味。","ingredients":["ロブスターテール — 2-3尾（各140-170g）","無塩バター（溶かす）— 大さじ3（42g）","にんにく（みじん切り）— 2-3片","レモン汁 — 大さじ1","黒コショウ — 小さじ1/2","パプリカ（飾り用、お好みで）"],"directions":["キッチンバサミで各ロブスターテールの背中の殻を中心に切り、尾扇の手前で止める。身を持ち上げて殻の上に置く。","小さなボウルに溶かしバター、にんにく、レモン汁、黒コショウを混ぜる。","ガーリックバターをロブスターの身にたっぷりと塗る。","尾をブロイラーパンに身を上にして並べる。","高温で6-10分、白く濁り軽く焦げ目がつくまで炙り焼く。"],"tips":["焼き過ぎ注意 — すぐにゴムのようになります。","6分経過後は注意深く見守る。"]},"pt":{"title":"Cauda de Lagosta Grelhada com Manteiga de Alho","description":"Elegantes caudas de lagosta pinceladas com manteiga de alho e grelhadas à perfeição — qualidade de restaurante em casa.","ingredients":["Caudas de lagosta — 2-3 caudas (cada 140-170 g)","Manteiga sem sal, derretida — 3 colheres de sopa (42 g)","Alho, picado — 2-3 dentes","Suco de limão — 1 colher de sopa","Pimenta preta — ½ colher de chá","Páprica (opcional, para decorar)"],"directions":["Usando tesoura de cozinha, corte através da casca superior de cada cauda pelo centro, parando no leque da cauda. Levante a carne e apoie-a sobre a casca.","Em uma tigela pequena, misture a manteiga derretida, alho, suco de limão e pimenta preta.","Pincele generosamente a mistura de manteiga de alho sobre a carne da lagosta.","Coloque as caudas na assadeira do grill, lado da carne para cima.","Grelhe em fogo alto por 6-10 minutos até ficar opaca e levemente tostada."],"tips":["Não cozinhe demais — a lagosta fica borrachuda rapidamente.","Observe atentamente após 6 minutos."]},"zh":{"title":"蒜香黄油烤龙虾尾","description":"优雅的龙虾尾涂满蒜香黄油，炙烤至完美 — 在家享受餐厅级美味。","ingredients":["龙虾尾 2-3只（每只约140-170克）","无盐黄油（融化）3汤匙（42克）","大蒜（切碎）2-3瓣","柠檬汁 1汤匙","黑胡椒 1/2茶匙","红椒粉（可选，装饰用）"],"directions":["用厨房剪刀从龙虾尾背壳正中剪开，剪至尾扇前停止。将龙虾肉翻出搁在壳上。","小碗中混合融化黄油、蒜末、柠檬汁和黑胡椒。","将蒜香黄油料慷慨地刷在龙虾肉上。","龙虾尾肉面朝上放入烤盘。","以高温炙烤6-10分钟，至虾肉变白不透明、表面微焦即可。"],"tips":["不要烤过头 — 龙虾会迅速变老变硬。","6分钟后盯紧。"]}}',
     7),
    ('airfryeroven', '🍪', 'Cookie', '320°F (160°C)', '11-13 minutes',
     '{"en":{"title":"Classic Chocolate Chip Cookies","description":"Soft, chewy chocolate chip cookies with perfectly golden edges — the timeless classic.","ingredients":["Unsalted butter, softened — ½ cup (113 g)","Granulated sugar — ⅓ cup (67 g)","Brown sugar, packed — ⅓ cup (70 g)","Egg — 1 large","All-purpose flour — 1½ cups (187 g)","Baking soda — 1 tsp","Salt — ½ tsp","Vanilla extract — 1 tsp","Chocolate chips — 1 cup (175 g)"],"directions":["In mixing bowl, beat softened butter with sugars until creamy.","Add egg and vanilla, mix until combined.","In separate bowl, whisk together flour, baking soda, and salt.","Gradually combine wet and dry ingredients together.","Fold in chocolate chips.","Drop rounded spoonfuls onto cookie sheet, spaced 2 inches apart.","Bake at 320°F (160°C) for 11-13 minutes until edges are golden."],"tips":["Chill dough 30+ minutes for thicker cookies.","Do not overbake — they continue cooking on the hot pan."]},"es":{"title":"Galletas Clásicas con Chispas de Chocolate","description":"Suaves y masticables galletas con chispas de chocolate con bordes perfectamente dorados — el clásico atemporal.","ingredients":["Mantequilla sin sal, ablandada — ½ taza (113 g)","Azúcar granulada — ⅓ taza (67 g)","Azúcar morena, compactada — ⅓ taza (70 g)","Huevo — 1 grande","Harina de trigo — 1½ tazas (187 g)","Bicarbonato de sodio — 1 cdta","Sal — ½ cdta","Extracto de vainilla — 1 cdta","Chispas de chocolate — 1 taza (175 g)"],"directions":["En un tazón, batir la mantequilla ablandada con los azúcares hasta que esté cremosa.","Agregar el huevo y la vainilla, mezclar hasta combinar.","En otro tazón, batir juntos la harina, bicarbonato y sal.","Combinar gradualmente los ingredientes húmedos y secos.","Incorporar las chispas de chocolate.","Colocar cucharadas redondeadas en la bandeja para galletas, espaciadas 5 cm.","Hornear a 160°C durante 11-13 minutos hasta que los bordes estén dorados."],"tips":["Enfriar la masa 30+ minutos para galletas más gruesas.","No hornear de más — continúan cocinándose en la bandeja caliente."]},"fr":{"title":"Cookies Classiques aux Pépites de Chocolat","description":"Cookies moelleuses aux pépites de chocolat avec des bords parfaitement dorés — le classique intemporel.","ingredients":["Beurre doux, ramolli — ½ tasse (113 g)","Sucre granulé — ⅓ tasse (67 g)","Cassonade, tassée — ⅓ tasse (70 g)","Œuf — 1 gros","Farine tout usage — 1½ tasses (187 g)","Bicarbonate de soude — 1 càc","Sel — ½ càc","Extrait de vanille — 1 càc","Pépites de chocolat — 1 tasse (175 g)"],"directions":["Dans un bol, battre le beurre ramolli avec les sucres jusqu à consistance crémeuse.","Ajouter l œuf et la vanille, mélanger.","Dans un autre bol, mélanger la farine, le bicarbonate et le sel.","Combiner progressivement les ingrédients humides et secs.","Incorporer les pépites de chocolat.","Déposer des cuillerées arrondies sur la plaque, espacées de 5 cm.","Cuire à 160°C pendant 11-13 minutes jusqu à ce que les bords soient dorés."],"tips":["Réfrigérer la pâte 30+ minutes pour des cookies plus épais.","Ne pas trop cuire — ils continuent à cuire sur la plaque chaude."]},"ja":{"title":"クラシックチョコチップクッキー","description":"ふんわりしっとり、縁は完璧なきつね色 — 時代を超えた定番クッキー。","ingredients":["無塩バター（常温）— ½カップ（113g）","グラニュー糖 — ⅓カップ（67g）","ブラウンシュガー（固く詰める）— ⅓カップ（70g）","卵 — 大1個","薄力粉 — 1½カップ（187g）","重曹 — 小さじ1","塩 — 小さじ½","バニラエッセンス — 小さじ1","チョコチップ — 1カップ（175g）"],"directions":["ボウルでバターと砂糖をクリーム状になるまで混ぜる。","卵とバニラを加えて混ぜる。","別のボウルで粉、重曹、塩を合わせる。","湿った材料と粉類を少しずつ合わせる。","チョコチップを折り込む。","スプーンで丸くすくって天板に並べ、5cm間隔を空ける。","320°F（160°C）で11-13分、縁がきつね色になるまで焼く。"],"tips":["厚めのクッキーにしたいなら生地を30分以上冷蔵で休ませる。","焼きすぎ注意 — 熱い天板の上で余熱調理が続きます。"]},"pt":{"title":"Cookies Clássicos de Chocolate","description":"Cookies macios de chocolate com bordas perfeitamente douradas — o clássico atemporal.","ingredients":["Manteiga sem sal, amolecida — ½ xícara (113 g)","Açúcar granulado — ⅓ xícara (67 g)","Açúcar mascavo, compactado — ⅓ xícara (70 g)","Ovo — 1 grande","Farinha de trigo — 1½ xícaras (187 g)","Bicarbonato de sódio — 1 colher de chá","Sal — ½ colher de chá","Extrato de baunilha — 1 colher de chá","Gotas de chocolate — 1 xícara (175 g)"],"directions":["Na tigela, bata a manteiga amolecida com os açúcares até ficar cremosa.","Adicione o ovo e a baunilha, misture.","Em outra tigela, misture a farinha, bicarbonato e sal.","Combine gradualmente os ingredientes úmidos e secos.","Incorpore as gotas de chocolate.","Coloque colheradas arredondadas na assadeira, espaçadas 5 cm.","Asse a 160°C por 11-13 minutos até as bordas dourarem."],"tips":["Refrigere a massa por 30+ minutos para cookies mais grossos.","Não asse demais — eles continuam cozinhando na assadeira quente."]},"zh":{"title":"经典巧克力曲奇","description":"外酥里软的巧克力曲奇，边缘金黄酥脆 — 永恒经典的味道。","ingredients":["无盐黄油（室温软化）1/2杯（113克）","白砂糖 1/3杯（67克）","红糖（压实）1/3杯（70克）","鸡蛋 1个（大）","中筋面粉 1.5杯（187克）","小苏打 1茶匙","盐 1/2茶匙","香草精 1茶匙","巧克力豆 1杯（175克）"],"directions":["将软化黄油与两种糖打发至蓬松奶油状。","加入鸡蛋和香草精，搅拌均匀。","另取碗将面粉、小苏打和盐混合。","将干湿材料逐步混合均匀。","拌入巧克力豆。","用勺子舀出圆球状，间隔5厘米放在烤盘上。","以320°F（160°C）烤11-13分钟，至边缘金黄即可。"],"tips":["面团冷藏30分钟以上可做出更厚实的曲奇。","不要烤过头 — 取出后烤盘余热会继续烘烤。"]}}',
     8),
    ('airfryeroven', '🍎', 'Dehydrate', '135°F (57°C)', '6-8 hours',
     '{"en":{"title":"Apple Chips with Cinnamon","description":"Naturally sweet, crispy apple chips dusted with cinnamon — a healthy snack made easy.","ingredients":["Apples — 2-3 medium apples (450-600 g total)","Ground cinnamon — ½ tsp","Lemon juice — 1 Tbsp (optional, to prevent browning)"],"directions":["Wash apples thoroughly. Peeling is optional.","Slice the apples into 2-3 mm thin slices using a knife or mandoline.","If desired, gently toss the apple slices with lemon juice to reduce oxidation.","Sprinkle the cinnamon evenly over the apple slices.","Arrange apple slices in a single layer on dehydrating tray or baking tray, avoiding overlap.","Place the tray into the oven and select Dehydrate mode.","Set the temperature to 135°F (57°C) and dehydrate for 6-8 hours.","Turn the slices once halfway through for even drying, if needed.","Remove when apple chips are fully dried and become crisp after cooling.","Allow to cool completely before serving or storing."],"tips":["Thinner slices will dry faster and produce crisper chips.","Drying time may vary depending on apple variety and moisture content; begin checking at 6 hours."]},"es":{"title":"Chips de Manzana con Canela","description":"Chips de manzana naturalmente dulces, crujientes y espolvoreadas con canela — un snack saludable y fácil.","ingredients":["Manzanas — 2-3 manzanas medianas (450-600 g)","Canela molida — ½ cdta","Jugo de limón — 1 cda (opcional, para evitar la oxidación)"],"directions":["Lavar bien las manzanas. Pelar es opcional.","Cortar las manzanas en rodajas finas de 2-3 mm usando un cuchillo o mandolina.","Si lo desea, mezclar suavemente las rodajas con jugo de limón para reducir la oxidación.","Espolvorear la canela uniformemente sobre las rodajas.","Colocar las rodajas en una sola capa en la bandeja de deshidratación o de horno, evitando superposición.","Colocar la bandeja en el horno y seleccionar modo Deshidratar.","Configurar la temperatura a 57°C y deshidratar durante 6-8 horas.","Voltear las rodajas a la mitad del tiempo para un secado uniforme si es necesario.","Retirar cuando las chips estén completamente secas y se vuelvan crujientes al enfriarse.","Dejar enfriar completamente antes de servir o almacenar."],"tips":["Las rodajas más finas se secarán más rápido y producirán chips más crujientes.","El tiempo de secado puede variar según la variedad de manzana y el contenido de humedad; comenzar a verificar a las 6 horas."]},"fr":{"title":"Chips de Pomme à la Cannelle","description":"Des chips de pomme naturellement sucrées, croustillantes et saupoudrées de cannelle — un en-cas sain et facile.","ingredients":["Pommes — 2-3 pommes moyennes (450-600 g)","Cannelle moulue — ½ càc","Jus de citron — 1 càs (optionnel, pour éviter le brunissement)"],"directions":["Bien laver les pommes. L épluchage est optionnel.","Couper les pommes en fines tranches de 2-3 mm à l aide d un couteau ou d une mandoline.","Si désiré, mélanger délicatement les tranches avec le jus de citron pour réduire l oxydation.","Saupoudrer la cannelle uniformément sur les tranches de pomme.","Disposer les tranches en une seule couche sur le plateau de déshydratation ou la plaque de cuisson, sans les superposer.","Placer le plateau dans le four et sélectionner le mode Déshydrater.","Régler la température à 57°C et déshydrater pendant 6-8 heures.","Retourner les tranches à mi-cuisson pour un séchage uniforme, si nécessaire.","Retirer lorsque les chips sont complètement séchées et deviennent croustillantes après refroidissement.","Laisser refroidir complètement avant de servir ou de conserver."],"tips":["Les tranches plus fines sèchent plus vite et produisent des chips plus croustillantes.","Le temps de séchage peut varier selon la variété de pomme et la teneur en humidité; commencer à vérifier à 6 heures."]},"ja":{"title":"シナモンアップルチップス","description":"自然な甘さのカリカリアップルチップスにシナモンをふりかけて — 手軽なヘルシースナック。","ingredients":["りんご — 中2-3個（合計450-600g）","シナモンパウダー — 小さじ½","レモン汁 — 大さじ1（変色防止用、オプション）"],"directions":["りんごをよく洗う。皮むきはお好みで。","包丁またはマンドリンで2-3mmの薄切りにする。","必要に応じて、レモン汁を軽く絡めて酸化を防ぐ。","シナモンをりんごスライスに均等に振りかける。","乾燥トレイまたは天板に重ならないように一層に並べる。","トレイをオーブンに入れ、脱水モードを選択する。","温度を135°F（57°C）に設定し、6-8時間乾燥させる。","必要に応じて、途中で一度裏返して均等に乾燥させる。","完全に乾燥し、冷めるとカリカリになったら取り出す。","完全に冷ましてから提供または保存する。"],"tips":["薄切りほど早く乾き、よりカリカリに仕上がります。","乾燥時間はりんごの品種や水分量によって異なります。6時間経過したら確認を始めましょう。"]},"pt":{"title":"Chips de Maçã com Canela","description":"Chips de maçã naturalmente doces, crocantes e polvilhadas com canela — um lanche saudável e fácil.","ingredients":["Maçãs — 2-3 maçãs médias (450-600 g)","Canela em pó — ½ colher de chá","Suco de limão — 1 colher de sopa (opcional, para evitar o escurecimento)"],"directions":["Lave bem as maçãs. Descascar é opcional.","Corte as maçãs em fatias finas de 2-3 mm usando uma faca ou mandolina.","Se desejar, misture delicadamente as fatias com suco de limão para reduzir a oxidação.","Polvilhe a canela uniformemente sobre as fatias de maçã.","Disponha as fatias em uma única camada na bandeja de desidratação ou assadeira, evitando sobreposição.","Coloque a bandeja no forno e selecione o modo Desidratar.","Ajuste a temperatura para 57°C e desidrate por 6-8 horas.","Vire as fatias na metade do tempo para secagem uniforme, se necessário.","Retire quando os chips estiverem completamente secos e ficarem crocantes após esfriar.","Deixe esfriar completamente antes de servir ou armazenar."],"tips":["Fatias mais finas secam mais rápido e produzem chips mais crocantes.","O tempo de secagem pode variar conforme a variedade da maçã e o teor de umidade; comece a verificar após 6 horas."]},"zh":{"title":"肉桂苹果脆片","description":"天然香甜、酥脆可口的苹果脆片，撒上肉桂粉 — 轻松做出的健康零食。","ingredients":["苹果 2-3个（中等大小，约450-600克）","肉桂粉 1/2茶匙","柠檬汁 1汤匙（可选，防止氧化变色）"],"directions":["将苹果洗净。去皮可选。","用刀或切片器将苹果切成2-3毫米的薄片。","如需防变色，可将苹果片轻轻拌入柠檬汁。","将肉桂粉均匀撒在苹果片上。","将苹果片单层平铺在脱水盘或烤盘上，避免重叠。","将托盘放入烤箱，选择脱水模式。","温度设为135°F（57°C），脱水6-8小时。","如需均匀干燥，中途可将苹果片翻面一次。","待苹果片完全干燥、冷却后变脆即可取出。","完全冷却后再食用或储存。"],"tips":["切得越薄干燥越快，成品也更酥脆。","干燥时间因苹果品种和含水量而异，建议6小时后开始检查。"]}}',
     9),
    ('airfryeroven', '🍕', 'Ferment', '95-100°F (35-38°C)', '1-2 hours',
     '{"en":{"title":"Pizza Dough Proofing","description":"Perfectly proofed pizza dough every time — your secret to a light, airy crust.","ingredients":["Pizza dough — 1 dough ball (250-300 g) prepared according to your preferred pizza dough recipe","Olive oil — a small amount, optional (to prevent sticking)"],"directions":["Shape the pizza dough into a smooth ball.","Lightly coat the surface with olive oil if desired to prevent drying.","Place the dough in a bowl and cover loosely with plastic wrap or a damp cloth.","Place the covered dough into the oven.","Select Ferment mode.","Set the temperature to 95-100°F (35-38°C).","Allow the dough to proof for 1-2 hours, or until it doubles in size.","Remove the dough and proceed with shaping and baking as desired."],"tips":["Do not set the temperature above 105°F (40°C), as excessive heat may reduce yeast activity.","Proofing time may vary depending on dough size, yeast amount, and ambient conditions."]},"es":{"title":"Fermentación de Masa de Pizza","description":"Masa de pizza perfectamente fermentada cada vez — tu secreto para una corteza ligera y esponjosa.","ingredients":["Masa de pizza — 1 bola de masa (250-300 g) preparada según tu receta preferida","Aceite de oliva — pequeña cantidad, opcional (para evitar que se pegue)"],"directions":["Dar forma a la masa en una bola suave.","Cubrir ligeramente la superficie con aceite de oliva si se desea para evitar que se seque.","Colocar la masa en un tazón y cubrir holgadamente con plástico o un paño húmedo.","Colocar la masa cubierta en el horno.","Seleccionar modo Fermentar.","Configurar la temperatura a 35-38°C.","Dejar fermentar la masa durante 1-2 horas, o hasta que duplique su tamaño.","Retirar la masa y proceder con el formado y horneado según se desee."],"tips":["No configurar la temperatura por encima de 40°C, ya que el exceso de calor puede reducir la actividad de la levadura.","El tiempo de fermentación puede variar según el tamaño de la masa, la cantidad de levadura y las condiciones ambientales."]},"fr":{"title":"Fermentation de la Pâte à Pizza","description":"Une pâte à pizza parfaitement fermentée à chaque fois — votre secret pour une croûte légère et aérienne.","ingredients":["Pâte à pizza — 1 boule de pâte (250-300 g) préparée selon votre recette préférée","Huile d olive — petite quantité, optionnelle (pour éviter que ça colle)"],"directions":["Façonner la pâte en une boule lisse.","Enduire légèrement la surface d huile d olive si désiré pour éviter le dessèchement.","Placer la pâte dans un bol et couvrir sans serrer avec du film plastique ou un torchon humide.","Placer la pâte couverte dans le four.","Sélectionner le mode Fermentation.","Régler la température à 35-38°C.","Laisser la pâte fermenter pendant 1-2 heures, ou jusqu à ce qu elle double de volume.","Retirer la pâte et procéder au façonnage et à la cuisson selon vos envies."],"tips":["Ne pas régler la température au-dessus de 40°C, car une chaleur excessive peut réduire l activité de la levure.","Le temps de fermentation peut varier selon la taille de la pâte, la quantité de levure et les conditions ambiantes."]},"ja":{"title":"ピザ生地の発酵","description":"毎回完璧に発酵したピザ生地 — 軽くてふわふわしたクラストの秘密。","ingredients":["ピザ生地 — 1玉（250-300g）、お好みのレシピで準備","オリーブオイル — 少量（くっつき防止、オプション）"],"directions":["ピザ生地を滑らかなボール状に丸める。","乾燥防止のため、お好みで表面にオリーブオイルを薄く塗る。","生地をボウルに入れ、ラップまたは湿った布巾でゆるく覆う。","覆った生地をオーブンに入れる。","発酵モードを選択する。","温度を95-100°F（35-38°C）に設定する。","生地が2倍の大きさになるまで1-2時間発酵させる。","生地を取り出し、お好みで成形・焼成に進む。"],"tips":["105°F（40°C）以上に設定しないでください — 高温は酵母の活動を弱めます。","発酵時間は生地のサイズ、酵母の量、環境条件によって異なります。"]},"pt":{"title":"Fermentação de Massa de Pizza","description":"Massa de pizza perfeitamente fermentada sempre — seu segredo para uma crosta leve e aerada.","ingredients":["Massa de pizza — 1 bola de massa (250-300 g) preparada conforme sua receita preferida","Azeite de oliva — pequena quantidade, opcional (para evitar que grude)"],"directions":["Modele a massa de pizza em uma bola lisa.","Cubra levemente a superfície com azeite se desejar, para evitar que resseque.","Coloque a massa em uma tigela e cubra frouxamente com plástico filme ou um pano úmido.","Coloque a massa coberta no forno.","Selecione o modo Fermentar.","Ajuste a temperatura para 35-38°C.","Deixe a massa fermentar por 1-2 horas, ou até dobrar de tamanho.","Retire a massa e prossiga com a modelagem e o cozimento conforme desejar."],"tips":["Não ajuste a temperatura acima de 40°C, pois o calor excessivo pode reduzir a atividade do fermento.","O tempo de fermentação pode variar conforme o tamanho da massa, quantidade de fermento e condições ambientais."]},"zh":{"title":"披萨面团醒发","description":"每次都能完美醒发的披萨面团 — 轻盈蓬松饼底的秘诀。","ingredients":["披萨面团 1个面团（250-300克），按您喜欢的配方准备","橄榄油 少许（可选，防粘）"],"directions":["将披萨面团揉成光滑的圆球。","如需防干，可在表面薄涂一层橄榄油。","将面团放入碗中，用保鲜膜或湿布松松地盖上。","将盖好的面团放入烤箱。","选择发酵模式。","温度设为95-100°F（35-38°C）。","让面团醒发1-2小时，或直至体积翻倍。","取出面团，按需进行整形和烘烤。"],"tips":["温度不要超过105°F（40°C），高温会抑制酵母活性。","醒发时间因面团大小、酵母用量和环境条件而异。"]}}',
     10)
) AS v(category, emoji, mode, temp, time, translations, display_order)
CROSS JOIN target_product tp;

-- ============================================================
-- Step 6: RLS policies (full setup)
-- ============================================================

-- is_admin helper
CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION public.is_admin()
RETURNS boolean
LANGUAGE sql
STABLE
SECURITY DEFINER
AS $$
  SELECT (nullif(current_setting('request.jwt.claims', true)::jsonb -> 'app_metadata' ->> 'role', '')) = 'admin';
$$;

-- Products RLS
ALTER TABLE IF EXISTS products ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Anyone can read products" ON products;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin insert products" ON products;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin update products" ON products;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin delete products" ON products;
CREATE POLICY "Anyone can read products" ON products FOR SELECT USING (true);
CREATE POLICY "Admin insert products" ON products FOR INSERT WITH CHECK (public.is_admin());
CREATE POLICY "Admin update products" ON products FOR UPDATE USING (public.is_admin()) WITH CHECK (public.is_admin());
CREATE POLICY "Admin delete products" ON products FOR DELETE USING (public.is_admin());

-- Recipes RLS
ALTER TABLE IF EXISTS recipes ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Anyone can read recipes" ON recipes;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin insert recipes" ON recipes;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin update recipes" ON recipes;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin delete recipes" ON recipes;
CREATE POLICY "Anyone can read recipes" ON recipes FOR SELECT USING (true);
CREATE POLICY "Admin insert recipes" ON recipes FOR INSERT WITH CHECK (public.is_admin());
CREATE POLICY "Admin update recipes" ON recipes FOR UPDATE USING (public.is_admin()) WITH CHECK (public.is_admin());
CREATE POLICY "Admin delete recipes" ON recipes FOR DELETE USING (public.is_admin());

-- FAQs RLS
ALTER TABLE IF EXISTS faqs ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin full access faqs" ON faqs;
CREATE POLICY "Admin full access faqs" ON faqs FOR ALL USING (public.is_admin()) WITH CHECK (public.is_admin());

-- Inquiries RLS
ALTER TABLE IF EXISTS inquiries ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Anyone can insert inquiries" ON inquiries;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin read inquiries" ON inquiries;
CREATE POLICY "Anyone can insert inquiries" ON inquiries FOR INSERT WITH CHECK (true);
CREATE POLICY "Admin read inquiries" ON inquiries FOR SELECT USING (public.is_admin());

-- Contact Info RLS
ALTER TABLE IF EXISTS contact_info ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Anyone can read contact_info" ON contact_info;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin update contact_info" ON contact_info;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin insert contact_info" ON contact_info;
CREATE POLICY "Anyone can read contact_info" ON contact_info FOR SELECT USING (true);
CREATE POLICY "Admin update contact_info" ON contact_info FOR UPDATE USING (public.is_admin()) WITH CHECK (public.is_admin());
CREATE POLICY "Admin insert contact_info" ON contact_info FOR INSERT WITH CHECK (public.is_admin());

-- Purchase Channels RLS
ALTER TABLE IF EXISTS purchase_channels ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin insert channels" ON purchase_channels;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin update channels" ON purchase_channels;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin delete channels" ON purchase_channels;
CREATE POLICY "Admin insert channels" ON purchase_channels FOR INSERT WITH CHECK (public.is_admin());
CREATE POLICY "Admin update channels" ON purchase_channels FOR UPDATE USING (public.is_admin()) WITH CHECK (public.is_admin());
CREATE POLICY "Admin delete channels" ON purchase_channels FOR DELETE USING (public.is_admin());

-- Site Settings RLS
ALTER TABLE IF EXISTS site_settings ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin update settings" ON site_settings;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin insert settings" ON site_settings;
CREATE POLICY "Admin update settings" ON site_settings FOR UPDATE USING (public.is_admin()) WITH CHECK (public.is_admin());
CREATE POLICY "Admin insert settings" ON site_settings FOR INSERT WITH CHECK (public.is_admin());

-- Orders RLS
ALTER TABLE IF EXISTS orders ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin read orders" ON orders;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin update orders" ON orders;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Admin delete orders" ON orders;
CREATE POLICY "Admin read orders" ON orders FOR SELECT USING (public.is_admin());
CREATE POLICY "Admin update orders" ON orders FOR UPDATE USING (public.is_admin()) WITH CHECK (public.is_admin());
CREATE POLICY "Admin delete orders" ON orders FOR DELETE USING (public.is_admin());

-- Social Links RLS
